{"data":[{"date":"21:56 04/08","title":"\"V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, Liverpool m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/robbie-fowler-nhan-xet-liverpool-mua-toi-se-rat-dang-so.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Robbie Fowler nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Liverpool m\u00f9a h\u00e8 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed l\u1eeda trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 Man Utd, Man City hay Dortmund.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Liverpool<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Liverpool cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 th\u00e1y 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Anh g\u1ed3m Chester, Trammere Rovers, Bury v\u00e0 Blackburn, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1ea1m ch\u00e1n Dortmund, Man Utd v\u00e0 Man City t\u1ea1i ICC 2018. The Kop d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u00f2n hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Napoli v\u00e0 Torino.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Robbie Fowler nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Liverpool m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Robbie Fowler nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Liverpool m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/robbie-fowler-nhan-xet-liverpool-mua-toi-se-rat-dang-so.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Robbie Fowler nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Liverpool m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Liverpool c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 174 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed1n b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng: Alisson Becker, Fabinho, Naby Keita v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri. C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, The Klopp c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League 2018-19.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Robbie Fowler nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Liverpool<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Liverpool l\u00e0m trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8, Robbie Fowler nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: \"T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 khi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edbc kia Liverpool ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt do \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i 'y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n' trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, khi kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i th\u1eed th\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Nh\u01b0ng khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0 Man Utd, Man City hay Napoli, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Liverpool c\u00f3 t\u00e2m th\u1ebf chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u00eam n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem Liverpool \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi\".</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Robbie Fowler l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool khi t\u1eebng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 171 b\u00e0n sau 330 tr\u1eadn. Sau khi gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7, Fowler t\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a d\u1eabn d\u1eaft CLB Muangthong United \u1edf Th\u00e1i Lan.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Liverpool h\u00e8 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/liverpool-vs-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-372-193724.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Liverpool vs Napoli 0h00 ng\u00e0y 5/8 (Giao h\u1eefu CLB)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-cua-everton-khang-dinh-khong-them-chap-liverpool-172-193715.html\">T\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Everton kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m ch\u1ea5p Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-liverpool-vs-napoli-00h00-ngay-58-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-172-193687.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Napoli 00h00 ng\u00e0y 5/8 (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/nhung-ngoi-sao-bong-da-suyt-lo-do-vi-lon-cham-188-193648.html\">Nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 su\u00fdt l\u1ee1 d\u1edf v\u00ec\u2026 l\u1edbn ch\u1eadm</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-giam-gia-ban-origi-172-193640.html\">Liverpool gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-hanh-dong-cuc-dep-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-193633.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a Alisson v\u1edbi Karius</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2002","checkdouble":"193729"},{"date":"21:54 04/08","title":"T\u00e2n binh Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh h\u00e0ng hot World Cup v\u1edbi Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/tan-binh-ngoai-hang-anh-muon-gianh-hang-hot-world-cup-voi-arsenal-va-liverpool.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Wolvehampton mu\u1ed1n mua Domagoj Vida c\u1ee7a Besiktas, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Vida</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Laurent Koscielny \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool, Wolvehampton mu\u1ed1n mua Domagoj Vida h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool, Wolvehampton mu\u1ed1n mua Domagoj Vida h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Vuot-mat-Arsenal-va-Liverpool,-Wolvehampton-muon-mua-Domagoj-Vida-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Domagoj Vida \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal theo \u0111u\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Liverpool, HLV Klopp \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7. Hi\u1ec7n Matip \u0111ang d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f2n Klavan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Lovren v\u00e0 Van Dijk.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-gui-loi-de-nghi-dau-tien-cho-vida-172-191991.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Domagoj Vida c\u1ee7a Besiktas</span>, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Arsenal nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi. Trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3, Vida c\u0169ng v\u1eeba ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Lovren h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Subasic, ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVida \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao, c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Arsenal ho\u1eb7c Liverpool s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Vida.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Wolvehampton c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Vida</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wolvehampton mu\u1ed1n mua Domagoj Vida c\u1ee7a Besiktas, t\u00e2n binh Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wolvehampton muon mua Vida\" title=\"Wolvehampton mu\u1ed1n mua Vida\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/vida.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wolvehampton mu\u1ed1n mua Vida</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Vida, Wolves ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 18 tri\u1ec7u euro, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Trong\u00a0tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Besiktas t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Vida l\u00ean 22 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Mirror, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Molineux Stadium \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Vida v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng n\u1ebfu c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Wolvehampton.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Vida mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Wolvehampton thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi Arsenal ho\u1eb7c Liverpool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2001","checkdouble":"193730"},{"date":"01:00 05/08","title":"Real Madrid 3-1 Juventus (KT): Los Blancos t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Lopetegui ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t g\u1ecdn \"B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/real-madrid-vs-juventus-tran-dau-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i The Blues \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Daniele Rugani</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 2 t\u00e2n binh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. HLV Maurizio Sarri kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi v\u1ee5 Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi v\u1ee5 Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/muc-tieu-so-1-bao-tin-buon-cho-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rugani l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, \u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea3 Gary Cahill v\u00e0 David Luiz \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Daniele Rugani l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 c\u00f9ng HLV Sarri \u1edf Empoli, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1edbi Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 cho Daniele Rugani, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 h\u1ecd g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 30, 36 v\u00e0 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Rugani t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/quan-chuc-chelsea-bay-toi-italia-chot-vu-rugani-172-192143.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani </span>th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i The Blues \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Rugani cua Juventus\" title=\"trung ve Rugani cua Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/Vi-sao-Chelsea-muon-mua-Daniele-Rugani-bang-moi-gia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Rugani b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Tuttosport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Rugani \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Massimiliano Allegri h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u01b0c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao m\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Leonardo Bonucci, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Rugani, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf l\u1ea1i thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi Chelsea theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Rugani \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2000","checkdouble":"193731"},{"date":"22:30 04/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/them-mot-doi-bong-muon-co-matteo-darmian.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Benfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Matteo Darmian l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Benfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Benfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-hau-ve-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Darmian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Jose Mourinho, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn anh ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin Matteo Darmian mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-hau-ve-mu-172-193679.html\" target=\"_blank\">Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Darmian</span>, Juventus, Roma v\u00e0 Napoli c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ef1u sao Torino.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi\u1ebfn Mourinho mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Darmian \u1edf l\u1ea1i, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n. Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Benfica mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Darmian</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Benfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Benfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Benfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Benfica-muon-co-Matteo-Darmian-cua-MU-o-He-2018-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Benfica mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Darmian\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Sun kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Benfica kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Darmian \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a v\u00e0 k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a 2018/19\u00a0tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u euro.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Benfica \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn M.U h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford mu\u1ed1n 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf so v\u1edbi Benfica, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng mua \u0111\u1ee9t Darmian. Hi\u1ec7n Mourinho \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n, ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c c\u1ef1u sao Torino c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1999","checkdouble":"193732"},{"date":"03:00 05/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP AC Milan vs Barca 07h05 ng\u00e0y 5/8 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/ac-milan-vs-barca-tran-dau-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp AC Milan vs Barca: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 AC Milan vs Barcelona tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018 l\u00fac 07h05 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 5/8.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN XUNG QUANH<br>\r\n- Theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Barca thua 6, th\u1eafng 4/10 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y g\u1eb7p Milan.<br>\r\n- Theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Milan th\u1eafng 6, thua 2/8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. <br>\r\n- Theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Barca thua 5, h\u00f2a 1, th\u1eafng 2/8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nT\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 1<br>\r\n6/8 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong hi\u1ec7p 1. 3/4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Milan c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean trong hi\u1ec7p 1. 9/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Barca x\u1ea3y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Do v\u1eady, hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 t\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\nBarcelona: Cillessen, Cucurella, Lenglet, Marlon, Semedo, Roberto, Collado, Arthur, Malcom, Munir, Aleix Vidal<br>\r\nMilan: Donnarumma, Calabria, Romagnoli, Musacchio, Abate, Locatelli, Kessie, Bonaventura, Calhanoglu, Suso, Andre Silva\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/1/barca-2-4-roma.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1998","checkdouble":"193733"},{"date":"22:30 04/08","title":"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/muc-tieu-so-1-bao-tin-buon-cho-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i The Blues \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Daniele Rugani</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 2 t\u00e2n binh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. HLV Maurizio Sarri kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi v\u1ee5 Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi v\u1ee5 Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/muc-tieu-so-1-bao-tin-buon-cho-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rugani l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, \u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea3 Gary Cahill v\u00e0 David Luiz \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Daniele Rugani l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 c\u00f9ng HLV Sarri \u1edf Empoli, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1edbi Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 cho Daniele Rugani, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 h\u1ecd g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 30, 36 v\u00e0 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Rugani t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/quan-chuc-chelsea-bay-toi-italia-chot-vu-rugani-172-192143.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani </span>th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i The Blues \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Rugani cua Juventus\" title=\"trung ve Rugani cua Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/Vi-sao-Chelsea-muon-mua-Daniele-Rugani-bang-moi-gia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Rugani b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Tuttosport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Rugani \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Massimiliano Allegri h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u01b0c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao m\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Leonardo Bonucci, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Rugani, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf l\u1ea1i thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi Chelsea theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Rugani \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1997","checkdouble":"193735"},{"date":"22:59 04/08","title":"HLV Emery quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u1ee9c t\u1eed Danny Welbeck","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2015/7/25/Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Unai Emery quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ea9y Danny Welbeck r\u1eddi Arsenal, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 do t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Welbeck v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Danny Welbeck thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Arsenal. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. X\u00e9t r\u1ed9ng ra, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ea9y Danny Welbeck r\u1eddi Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ea9y Danny Welbeck r\u1eddi Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/HLV-Unai-Emery-quyet-tam-day-Danny-Welbeck-roi-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danny Welbeck v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nQu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u sao M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n, m\u00f9a t\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf anh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu Lacazette v\u00e0 Aubameyang. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 16 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thanh l\u00fd.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, khi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Emirates c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, t\u00f4i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u cho Arsenal, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n\u00a0c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Arsenal. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u1eaft HLV m\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Emery quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ea9y Welbeck ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, song Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y anh ra \u0111i b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"welbeck\" title=\"welbeck\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Danny-Welbeck-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-sap-bi-bat-bai-khoi-Arsenal-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Welbeck</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ea9y Danny Welbeck r\u1eddi Arsenal, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 do t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV PSG mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Welbeck \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y kinh ph\u00ed chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Steven Nzonzi t\u1eeb Sevilla. Hi\u1ec7n Everton \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t khao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Welbeck th\u00ec David Ospina v\u00e0 Lucas Perez c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Arsenal. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Petr Cech v\u00e0 Leno. HLV Emery c\u0169ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eb1ng anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f2n v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Lucas Perez, Arsenal ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 5 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. T\u1edd A Bola c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chap-nhan-ban-tien-dao-voi-gia-re-kho-tin-172-193725.html\" target=\"_blank\">Sporting Lisbon \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Lucas Perez</span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1996","checkdouble":"193736"},{"date":"23:35 04/08","title":"Ivan Perisic l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn MU \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/ivan-perisic-lai-khien-mu-dung-ngoi-khong-yen.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Perisic l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Mourinho \u0111\u1ec1u \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Juan Mata. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00f2n vai khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n MU quan t\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n MU quan t\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/ivan-perisic-lai-khien-mu-dung-ngoi-khong-yen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Perisic l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic c\u1ee7a Inter Milan. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi 3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 34, 38 v\u00e0 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kham n\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Perisic sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Inter Milan.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Perisic ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Inter, t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Croatia, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn M.U n\u1ed1i\u00a0l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-chot-perisic-thay-martial-172-192116.html\" target=\"_blank\">M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Perisic</span> \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Inter Milan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Perisic c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Perisic l\u1ea1i \u201cth\u1ea3 th\u00ednh\u201d M.U</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ivan Perisic dang nhan duoc su quan tam tu phia MU.\" title=\"Ivan Perisic \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda MU.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/13/MU-chuan-bi-ke-hoach-mua-tien-ve-Ivan-Perisic-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ivan Perisic mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u0103m ngo\u00e1i t\u00f4i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Inter, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i CLB. \u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2010 \u0111\u1ebfn nay ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A, song Inter \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nghe \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i CLB mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Inter \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNgo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 HLV t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec1u thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u00f3. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed s\u1ee9c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1995","checkdouble":"193738"},{"date":"06:28 05/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/8: L\u1ed9 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 M.U s\u1edf h\u1eefu Alderweireld","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/31/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-58-lo-muc-gia-de-mu-so-huu-alderweireld.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 5/8.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nL\u1ed9 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 M.U s\u1edf h\u1eefu Alderweireld<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd Mirror, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Tottenham, n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f2i 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng M.U bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Alderweireld ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau, khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2020.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/8 L\u1ed9 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 MU s\u1edf h\u1eefu Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 58 L\u1ed9 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 MU s\u1edf h\u1eefu Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/Truoc-nhung-tin-don-Toby-Alderweireld-phat-bieu-ve-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/8: L\u1ed9 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 M.U s\u1edf h\u1eefu Alderweireld</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Perisic l\u1ea1i th\u1ea3 th\u00ednh M.U</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, anh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb &ldquo;m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng&rdquo;, v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n th\u1eed s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh \u1edf Premier League. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Ivan Perisic cho bi\u1ebft v\u1eabn h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Inter, v\u00e0 anh kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Milan t\u00ednh ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu 2 ng\u00f4i sao l\u00e0 Higuain v\u00e0 Calfara t\u1eeb Juventus, Rossoneri ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i h\u1ecfi mua sao tr\u1ebb Sergej Milinkovic-Savic. Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Lazio v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u euro, c\u00f9ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn mua \u0111\u1ee9t gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0o m\u00f9a sau. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Savic l\u00ean t\u1edbi 120 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Inter th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Modric<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 x\u00fac ti\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, c\u00f2n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Croatia c\u0169ng h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Modric l\u00e0 750 tri\u1ec7u euro, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh \u0111i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/8\" title=\"Modric v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-257-MU-tong-tan-cong-Willian-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/8: Modric \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Inter</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal s\u1eafp b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb qu\u00ean l\u00e3ng t\u1ea1i Emirates &ndash; Lucas Perez \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi h\u1ecfi mua t\u1eeb Sporting Lisbon v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb m\u1ea1t: 4,45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y, khi nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1994","checkdouble":"193743"},{"date":"06:42 05/08","title":"Alisson ra m\u1eaft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/5/alisson-ra-mat-thanh-cong-klopp-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Napoli, HLV Jurgen Klopp h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 Alisson \u2013 bom t\u1ea5n 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nKlopp h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Alisson<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat trong m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft The Kop, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong khung g\u1ed7, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi. Alisson \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Napoli ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2m l\u1eb7ng, khi nh\u1eefng Milner, Wijnaldum, Salah, Sturridge v\u00e0 Moreno l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u01a1t ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Jurgen Klopp cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Liverpool. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c m\u00e0 Alisson ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn trong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau khi \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft ra.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 Alisson trong m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 Alisson trong m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/ali.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Jurgen Klopp h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Napoli, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi 100% s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Alisson bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ee9ng trong khung g\u1ed7. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o c\u00e1ch l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Alisson, v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i quen v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3. B\u1ea1n thua \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n sai, ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea1n th\u1eafng 5-0 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i l\u00ean r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay&rdquo; &ndash; Jurgen Klopp h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 Alisson.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-50-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-329-193740.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/video-tong-hop-liverpool-50-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-50-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-329-193740.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Liverpool 5-0 Napoli (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/liverpool-vs-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-372-193724.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/liverpool-vs-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/liverpool-vs-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-372-193724.html\">Liverpool 5-0 Napoli: The Klopp h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Serie A trong ng\u00e0y Alisson ra m\u1eaft</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1993","checkdouble":"193744"},{"date":"13:14 04/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PSV Eindhoven vs Feyenoord 23h00 ng\u00e0y 4/8 (Si\u00eau c\u00fap H\u00e0 Lan 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/nhan-dinh-psv-eindhoven-vs-feyenoord-23h00-ngay-48-sieu-cup-ha-lan-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSV Eindhoven vs Feyenoord l\u00fac 23h00 ng\u00e0y 4/8 (Si\u00eau c\u00fap H\u00e0 Lan 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PSV Eindhoven vs Feyenoord 23h ng\u00e0y 48 Si\u00eau c\u00fap H\u00e0 Lan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PSV Eindhoven vs Feyenoord 23h ng\u00e0y 48 Si\u00eau c\u00fap H\u00e0 Lan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/PSV-Eindhoven-vs-Feyenoord.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">PSV Eindhoven vs Feyenoord</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span>PSV Eindhoven vs Feyenoord: 3-1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f2n kh\u00f3 g\u1ea5p b\u1ed9i. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Feyenoord hi\u1ec3u qu\u00e1 r\u00f5 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd n\u00e0y khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc PSV Eindhoven trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch H\u00e0 Lan m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 4 chung cu\u1ed9c, k\u00e9m PSV t\u1edbi 17 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c an \u1ee7i ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o khi gi\u00e0nh c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia H\u00e0 Lan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00eam nay, PSV v\u00e0 Feyenoord s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn tranh si\u00eau c\u00fap H\u00e0 Lan di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Philipps c\u1ee7a PSV. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, PSV Eindhoven \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t 3 ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Joshua Brenet, Santiago Arias v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Marco van Ginkel. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 H\u00e0 Lan c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng suy gi\u1ea3m m\u1ea5y. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mark Van Bommel \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Feyenoord c\u0169ng c\u00f3 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng (th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 1, thua 1). M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t: s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Ch\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2u xa, 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y Feyenoord m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd: ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jordi Clasie (Southampton). Ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u00edt \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh si\u00eau c\u00fap H\u00e0 Lan v\u1edbi PSV. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng trong 4 chuy\u1ebfn vi\u1ebfng th\u0103m s\u00e2n Philipps g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 3 l\u1ea7n n\u1ebfm m\u00f9i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCc\u1ea3 PSV v\u00e0 Feyenoord \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- PSV Eindhoven th\u1eafng 5/8 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Feyenoord g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng (th\u1eafng 5, thua 3).<br>\r\n- 5/7 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n- PSV Eindhoven th\u1eafng 3/4 cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Feyenoord g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ PSV Eindhoven: Zoet - Dumfries, Schwaab, Viergever, Angelino - Hendrix, Rosario, Pereiro - Malen, L.De Jong, Bergwijn.<br>\r\n+ Feyenoord: Bijlow - Jusste, Botteghin, Van der Heijden, Malacia, Toornstra, Wehrmann, Vilhena, Berghuis, Van Persie, Larsson.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1992","checkdouble":"193700"},{"date":"13:23 04/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Porto vs Aves 02h45 ng\u00e0y 5/8 (Si\u00eau C\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/nhan-dinh-porto-vs-aves-02h45-ngay-58-sieu-cup-bo-dao-nha-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Porto vs Aves l\u00fac 02h45 ng\u00e0y 5/8 (Si\u00eau C\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha B\u0110N 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Porto vs Aves 02h45 ng\u00e0y 58 Si\u00eau C\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Porto vs Aves 02h45 ng\u00e0y 58 Si\u00eau C\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/Porto-vs-Aves.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Porto vs Aves</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Porto vs Aves: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>N\u0103m nay l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 40 Si\u00eau C\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c. Porto \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 20 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap n\u00e0y, b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee9ng ngay sau tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0ng t\u1edbi 12 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u0103ng quang (Sporting Lisbon ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 8 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch). N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh ri\u00eang v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap B\u0110N, Porto \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i 29 trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 39 l\u1ea7n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ea5y kinh nghi\u1ec7m d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Aves g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau C\u00fap B\u0110N. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Aves l\u1eadp n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch khi c\u00f3 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia sau khi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sporting Lisbon \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch kh\u00f3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 c\u1ee7a Aves ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1eabn l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG khi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 \"ch\u1ebft h\u1ee5t\" v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 13 tr\u00ean 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Aves \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7i lo khi ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0o trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, Aves c\u00e0ng kh\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Porto.</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1991","checkdouble":"193701"},{"date":"14:07 04/08","title":"Barca c\u00f3 Vidal, Valverde vui nh\u01b0 \u201cm\u1edf c\u1edd trong b\u1ee5ng\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-ve-vidal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (4/8). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2>M.U l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Savic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Italia cho bi\u1ebft, Lazio \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Milinkovic-Savic t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c MU, v\u00e0 hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMU \u0111ang g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, khi c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau quan tr\u1ecdng lu\u00f4n t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia nh\u1eadp s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, MU \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Lazio \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic, khi m\u00e0 m\u00f9a chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Premier League ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 48, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 48, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-107,-tin-nong-chuyen-nhuong-he-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, G\u0110TT Tare x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Lazio \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Milinkovic-Savic.Lazio t\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 80 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 Juventus \u0111\u01b0a ra. Tare cho bi\u1ebft, CLB mu\u1ed1n con s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 120 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede World Cup 2018, d\u00f9 Serbia kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, nh\u01b0ng Milinkovic-Savic v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. Anh l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Barca tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c gia World Cup</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00cdt gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1ee5 Vidal, Barca th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal Moussa Wague t\u1eeb CLB KAS Eupen. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i Barca. Ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. Theo t\u1edd Sport (T\u00e2y Ban Nha), Wague s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i Barca B.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWague g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tu\u1ed5i teen th\u1ee9 hai l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, sau Kylian Mbappe c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. \u1ede 19 tu\u1ed5i 263 ng\u00e0y, Wague c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00e2u Phi tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng World Cup.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 48 MU l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Savic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 48 MU l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Savic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-48-MU-lai-day-nhanh-thuong-vu-Savic-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Moussa Wague</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Iwobi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110\u00eam qua, Arsenal th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o Alex Iwobi \u0111\u00e3 cam k\u1ebft d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. D\u00f9 Arsenal kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 chi ti\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng, theo Daily Mail, Alex Iwobi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi CLB ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates th\u00eam 4 n\u0103m n\u1eefa. Alex Iwobi gia nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n tr\u1ebb Arsenal t\u1eeb n\u0103m m\u1edbi 9 tu\u1ed5i. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2015 t\u1edbi nay, Iwobi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 98 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/iwobi-dong-y-gia-han-voi-arsenal-172-192029.html\">N\u00d3NG: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Joe Hart s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Burnley v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb \"The Citizen\". HLV Sean Dyche mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn sau khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Pope bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n. Joe Hart t\u1eebng l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh nh\u01b0ng d\u1ea7n m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Hart\" title=\"thu mon Hart\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/Joe-Hart-toi-Burnley-voi-gia-4-trieu-bang-tu-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Joe Hart</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus, CLB Serie A c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh \u201cRonaldo\u201d</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau khi Juventus ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng bom t\u1ea5n tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mang t\u00ean Cristiano Ronaldo, m\u1ed9t CLB kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i Serie A l\u00e0 Sampdoria c\u0169ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean Ronaldo, nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 Ronaldo Vieira.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i khi trang Twitter c\u1ee7a Sampdoria \u0111\u0103ng h\u00ecnh th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u00e2n binh gi\u1ed1ng h\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch Juventus l\u00e0m khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu CR7. C\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef Ronaldo c\u00e1ch \u0111i\u1ec7u m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n \u0111en. Ch\u1ec9 kh\u00e1c r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo c\u1ee7a Sampdoria c\u00f3 th\u00eam ch\u1eef \"Vieira\" b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>\u201cVua t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9\u201d b\u1eadt b\u00e3i kh\u1ecfi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Chuba Akpom gia nh\u1eadp CLB PAOK Salonika (Hy L\u1ea1p). Th\u00f4ng tin tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Arsenal c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7. Theo \u0111\u00f3, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb 22 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00ed b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi PAOK Salonika. Chuba Akpom l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Arsenal. Anh gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2002, khi m\u1edbi l\u00ean 6. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y ra \u0111i, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 16 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1990","checkdouble":"193703"},{"date":"14:42 04/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t sao tr\u1ebb Man City chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp CLB h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/lucas-nmecha-sap-roi-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lucas Nmecha s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Sao tr\u1ebb U19 Anh r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd theo ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jack Harrison t\u1edbi Leeds United c\u1ee7a HLV Marcelo Bielsa.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Guardiola th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Bielsa</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Pep Guardiola l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i Marcelo Bielsa. \u00d4ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Argentina c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh. Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, c\u00e1ch b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Guardiola hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb Bielsa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do sau khi Bielsa t\u1edbi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Leeds United, Guardiola d\u00e0nh cho \u00f4ng nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u01b0u \u00e1i. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Man City \u0111\u1ec3 Jack Harrison t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Elland Road d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Nmecha s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lucas Nmecha s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Lucas-Nmecha-sap-roi-Man-City-duoi-dang-cho-muon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Guardiola th\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng Bielsa c\u1ee7a Leeds</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGuardiola tin r\u1eb1ng phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Leeds s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Man City. Do \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m qu\u00fd b\u00e1u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nmecha s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Leeds</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGuardiola s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho Leeds m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Man City n\u1eefa. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Lucas Nmecha s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Bielsa d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Man City v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Nmecha cua Man City\" title=\"Lucas Nmecha cua Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/lucas-nmecha-sap-roi-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nmecha s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNmecha sinh cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 1998, t\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 20 tu\u1ed5i. Anh sinh t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c song gia nh\u1eadp l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Man City khi m\u1edbi 9 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Anh, Nmecha c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 30 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Leeds, nh\u1eefng Swansea, Blackburn v\u00e0 West Brom t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng ng\u1ecf l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Nmecha. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft gi\u1eefa hai HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng West Yorkshire v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/guardiola-phat-bieu-ve-harrison-172-192399.html\">Guardiola m\u1edf c\u1eeda cho sao tr\u1ebb Man City ra \u0111i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-chot-gia-ban-day-bat-ngo-cho-joe-hart-172-192394.html\">Man City ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho Joe Hart</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-chieu-mo-sao-juventus-172-192204.html\">Pep Guardiola l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hanh-dong-nay-cua-john-stones-khien-pep-mung-roi-nuoc-mat-172-192039.html\">H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a John Stones khi\u1ebfn Pep m\u1eebng r\u01a1i n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-mua-kante-neu-mat-pjanic-vao-tay-man-city-172-191995.html\">V\u00ec Man City, Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Kante v\u00e0o tay Juventus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1989","checkdouble":"193705"},{"date":"15:14 04/08","title":"Bayern c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/zambrano-phat-bieu-ve-tan-binh-bayern-alphonso-davies.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Octavio Zambrano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Bayern Munich, Alphonso Davies. C\u1ef1u HLV Canada tin Bayern \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 19 tri\u1ec7u Euro n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Davies</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 7 v\u1eeba qua, Bayern Munich c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 19 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1edbi Alphonso Davies c\u1ee7a Vancouver Whitecaps. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 18 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y (sinh th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m 2000) s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Canada t\u1edbi h\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS n\u0103m 2018 r\u1ed3i m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Bayern v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2019.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBayern s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 ngay cho Vancouver Whitecaps s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 11,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro. T\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh t\u00edch, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d tr\u1ea3 cho \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mua Alphonso Davies c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean 19 tri\u1ec7u Euro, k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c b\u00e1n \u0111i c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i MLS.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zambrano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Bayern, Alphonso Davies h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Zambrano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Bayern, Alphonso Davies h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/zambrano-phat-bieu-ve-tan-binh-bayern-alphonso-davies.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Zambrano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Bayern, Davies</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y c\u0169 ng\u1ee3i khen sao tr\u1ebb</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlphonso Davies mang g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c Liberia, sinh t\u1ea1i Ghana song l\u1ea1i s\u1edbm chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Canada ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Vancouver Whitecaps. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau khi c\u00f3 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Canada, anh \u0111\u00e3 ra m\u1eaft \u0110TQG n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 16, m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y c\u0169 t\u1ea1i \u0110T Canada, Octavio Zambrano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Bayern Munich, Alphonso Davies v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 60 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 19 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1eabn l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 h\u1eddi cho sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bayern-khong-muon-mua-martial-172-193655.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/bayern-khong-muon-mua-martial.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bayern-khong-muon-mua-martial-172-193655.html\">Bayern t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i thanh l\u00fd sao v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt gi\u00fap M.U</span><br>\r\n<span>Bayern kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Martial. Ch\u00ednh ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Karl-Heinz Rummenigge c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Bild.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cBayern \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi, kh\u00f4ng nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec n\u1eefa. 100% \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt\u201d, Zambrano n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u1edd Goal. \u201cNh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng th\u0103ng hoa nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Alphonso Davies v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Davies ph\u1ea3i g\u1ea5p 3 t\u1edbi 4 l\u1ea7n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay, Davies c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n cho \u0110T Canada ch\u1ec9 sau 6 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o. Sao tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i teen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i C\u00fap v\u00e0ng CONCACAF 2017 v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1edbi Bayern. HLV Zambrano kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a tr\u00f2 c\u0169.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Davies l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cL\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam nh\u1ea1y b\u00e9n \u1edf 1/3 cu\u1ed1i s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi so v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Bayern Munich tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich-180-193675.html\">Barca CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern Munich</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bayern-munich-ngay-lap-tuc-ban-jerome-boateng-cho-mu-neu-172-192625.html\">Bayern Munich ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u00e1n Jerome Boateng cho MU n\u1ebfu....</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barcelona-dat-thoa-thuan-chieu-mo-arturo-vidal-180-192611.html\">\u0110\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Barca s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Arturo Vidal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/bayern-munich-mia-mai-juventus-phi-tien-vi-ong-gia-ronaldo-176-192582.html\">Bayern Munich m\u1ec9a mai Juventus ph\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u00ec \u201c\u00f4ng gi\u00e0\u201d Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-co-150-trieu-euro-cung-dung-mo-lewandowski-180-192443.html\">Real Madrid c\u00f3 150 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 Lewandowski</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1988","checkdouble":"193707"}]}